  cors:
    allowed-origins: "*"
    allowed-methods: GET,HEAD,POST,PUT,DELETE,OPTIONS
    allowed-headers: *
    allow-credentials: true
    max-age: 86400
```

2. 开启服务器，前端代码中直接访问接口即可。

```js
